race.comment: Strong race with some progressive types engaged. BIRD WHISTLE (9) heavily supported on debut as favourite when a dominant winner over 1200m here last July. Fitted with the two trials and can continue where she left off last time. FAVOUR THE BOLD (1) justified the short price ($1.30 fav), when a determined maiden winner over 1000m at this track. Sparingly raced and has more to offer. Gets map favours today. CHICA DEL MAR (3) unplaced in two runs back and again missed the frame last start over 1200m at Port Macquarie. Smart when right and looking for the 1300m now. ELLOFADUDE (6) up in grade from the wide gate when an eye catching third over 1200m at Port Macquarie. Visors go on and will race much closer to the speed.
